metadata.name: Imaginary Girl
metadata.description:
This is me in the lost tumult of colors, a deep image is hidden in my dreams, sometimes I see myself in hidden fantasies, yes, I am a fantasy from the past, maybe the future, depending on this body, I can neither get rid of this devil in prison nor thisÂ  The demon will be released from me, maybe we are all imaginary, each color in different images.
Digital painting
